<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_1383179_tradenow.CustomUserUtils</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>CustomUserUtils</name><script><![CDATA[var CustomUserUtils = Class.create();
CustomUserUtils.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {},

    getUserData: function() {
        var user = gs.getUser();
        if (user) {
            var userData = {
                first_name: user.getFirstName(),
                last_name: user.getLastName(),
                email: user.getEmail(),
                department: user.getDepartment(),
                
            };
            return JSON.stringify(userData);
        }
        return '';
    },

    type: 'CustomUserUtils'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>jagriti</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2024-04-23 06:16:46</sys_created_on><sys_id>3d8dea648371c610edb56060ceaad382</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>CustomUserUtils</sys_name><sys_package display_value="TradeNow" source="x_1383179_tradenow">48d5320c837d0610edb56060ceaad314</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="TradeNow">48d5320c837d0610edb56060ceaad314</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_3d8dea648371c610edb56060ceaad382</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>jagriti</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-04-23 06:16:46</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
